{"tid":1699354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"殺人政權 天理不容 三罷開花 刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-11-08T04:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:45:27.000Z","uid":3145,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e54879a2b1f83901e9f695517ad27352f3ac210","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"除左周梓樂<br />\n11月3 天水圍墮樓少年<br />\n100毛女主播<br />\n尋日旺角單嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oufanFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoufanFV.jpg&h=8ff6748f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同隔離棟樓遠到閪咁 我當佢跳遠高手 頭嘅方向都只會係向H&amp;M 而唔會係西洋菜街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvHPDef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvHPDef.jpg&h=e4bf2861&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而事實就係真係唔係向H&amp;M<br />\n身上有棍傷 係咪警棍?<br />\n狗賊會同你講死因無可疑<br />\n而家港共政權已經開始殺人如麻<br />\n我無嘢講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔鼓勵大家做任何咩 我無煽動</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>總之祝大家武運昌隆</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a1c5ecdc0934d2d3629f1ca196f7455916cde514","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"武運昌隆x1"},{"pid":"daaf03a4933fbabf8b357f3dded50188213b05fd","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"武運昌隆x2"},{"pid":"73ee0d74b0838cc121fb13428d87095aaf6b57ac","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"武運昌隆x3"},{"pid":"75a1bae79e33f3f6a48485efcce717eb04d576da","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"武運昌隆x4"},{"pid":"a1a28cf0c895e213ec4a94502445d0b3fdafe032","tid":1699354,"uid":3145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"武運昌隆x5"},{"pid":